IS S'PORE CRAZY TO NAME WAR MUSEUM SYONAN, A NAME GIVEN BY OUR JAP INVADERS?   Advertisement 
<Facebook post by Tan Wah-Piow> 
WHO IN THE RIGHT MIND WOULD NAME A MUSEUM SYONAN - Syonan-To is the name for Singapore given by the Japanese invaders. 
WHO IN THE RIGHT MIND WOULD TIME THE OPENING OF THE MUSEUM TO CELEBRATE THE ANNIVERSARY OF JAPAN'S INVASION OF SINGAPORE? Editor's Note:
